cs.PL, cs.AR, cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.SY

This paper discusses a technique for optimizing programs at run-time based on their behavior, which falls under the category of program analysis and optimization (cs.PL). It also involves monitoring program behavior (cs.AR) and adapting to changing environments (cs.SY). The use of machine learning techniques for selecting the best code versions suggests a focus on software engineering (cs.SE) and possibly also on machine learning (cs.LG).
